title: Top Places to visit in Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh
content: Jabalpur (formerly known as Jubbulpore, the official spelling until 2006) is a tier 2 city in the state of Madhya Pradesh, India. It is one of the major cities of Madhya Pradesh.
